    <item>
      <title>再生元制药遭遇法律挫折 遭遇两年来最糟糕一个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/regeneron-regn-set-for-big-monthly-drop-on-amgen-amgn-biosimilar-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[再生元制药公司 (Regeneron Pharmaceuticals Inc.) 股价有望创下 2022 年中以来的最大月度跌幅，原因是该公司遭遇法律挫折，这为提前推出与该制药商的重磅眼科治疗药物 Eylea 竞争的疗法打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/regeneron-regn-set-for-big-monthly-drop-on-amgen-amgn-biosimilar-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:48:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BNEF：到 2050 年实现净零排放？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-27/bnef-net-zero-emissions-by-2050-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，纽约将举办今年迄今为止规模最大的气候会议。彭博新能源财经能源经济团队助理 Rodrigo Quintero 在“彭博日报：欧洲”节目中探讨了未来十年可能的发展方向。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-27/bnef-net-zero-emissions-by-2050-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:42:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街交易员在并购中奉行简化原则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-27/wall-street-dealmakers-play-simplification-theme-in-m-a-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Crystal Tse 报道了随着企业从寻求多元化转向简化业务，交易方式发生转变的情况。Tse 在“彭博未平仓合约”中表示，曾经推动整合的银行家正从分拆和资产出售趋势中受益。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-27/wall-street-dealmakers-play-simplification-theme-in-m-a-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:32:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债有望实现 2010 年以来最长的月度上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/bonds-rise-as-mild-inflation-backs-case-for-another-big-fed-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储力求实现罕见的软着陆，交易商押注利率将进一步下调半个百分点，美国国债有望创下 14 年来最长的月度连续上涨势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/bonds-rise-as-mild-inflation-backs-case-for-another-big-fed-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 13:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无论有没有欧盟，英国都计划在 2027 年实现 T+1 转换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/uk-targets-shift-to-t-1-trading-in-2027-regardless-of-eu-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[牵头推动英国转向更快贸易机制的组织正在为英国在欧盟之前实现转变的可能性做准备，此举可能给整个地区的金融专业人士带来一系列麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/uk-targets-shift-to-t-1-trading-in-2027-regardless-of-eu-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 12:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
